  "short_description": "This is a first-person 3D adventure puzzle game featuring a female protagonist, inspired by modern work stress and related psychological issues. Players dive into the game, using \"Aperture\" to unravel layers of mystery, and uncover the inner strength and beautiful memories of life deep within.",
